ActCanada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Labour of HAROLD CALLA of North Vancouver, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Grace Kwok, whose term has expired.
